{"tid":2202920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"差人供詞三版本 認「有機會記錯」","createTime":"2020-09-15T03:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T03:51:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a22c62593e1a1a1abaca176bbd0dc582a24d37b","tid":2202920,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/PDOQ7EJBTJDFPPSI2WKYNOKV4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FPDOQ7EJBTJDFPPSI2WKYNOKV4U%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=b90edc3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FPDOQ7EJBTJDFPPSI2WKYNOKV4U%2F&h=7032ab3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/PDOQ7EJBTJDFPPSI2WKYNOKV4U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n差人供詞三版本 認「有機會記錯」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0Rzb8DPPhGvd5gbx7bDSHNIsSOU=/582x582/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AEB75BGHCZA3HJQA3C7RCZIGAE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0Rzb8DPPhGvd5gbx7bDSHNIsSOU%3D%2F582x582%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAEB75BGHCZA3HJQA3C7RCZIGAE.jpg&h=0f33a35d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【社工暴動案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8.31港島警民衝突中，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問警員陳澤鈞（圖）時指出，陳庭上作供與筆錄口供有多處不一致，例如陳的筆錄口供只提到「四周有人大叫」，口號是「光復香港、時代革命」等，但三份口供均沒有提及他庭上所稱的「死黑警、黑警死全家」口號。陳同意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱遭記者包圍 與片段不符<br />\n<br />\n辯方又質疑陳就截停被告的經過，曾供出三個不同版本。對於陳在庭上供稱，拘捕首被告時記者一擁而上包圍，使他未能施行警誡；辯方重播現場片段，當時一名警長向在場記者說「慢慢影，唔會阻你」，直指完全沒有陳所描述的情況。陳起初不同意，隨後承認「有機會記錯」。<br />\n<br />\n陳又指截停首被告，是因他或干犯非法集結，「對警方表示威嚇，憎恨我哋警察」，否認不斷改口供或作古仔。<br />\n<br />\n另外，協助控制次被告的警員李家豪供稱，當日跑到中國海外中心時，一名速龍成員正壓低一名嫌疑犯，故他隨即上前協助押解。主控官一度稱警員當時正壓低一名「示威人士」，法官沈小民質疑稱呼是否恰當：「用『人』得唔得呢？」主控最終修改發問字眼。審訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC12/20"},{"pid":"5ced558263fa552246b0add9640c43736460dab8","tid":2202920,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"誠實可靠，冇夾口供"},{"pid":"fee5cb1ce39e5a8cc455b05359f793f1a847581f","tid":2202920,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ced558263fa552246b0add9640c43736460dab8","tid":2202920,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"誠實可靠，冇夾口供"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:51:05.000Z","msg":"同一個人嚟"}]}